DA is 10% of Basic Salary.
TA is 20% of Basic Salary.

GS = Basic Salary + HRA + DA + TA;

TAX DEDUCTION is 10% of GS.

NS = GS - TAX DEDUCTION.

NOte : Use Basic Salary in Lexical Scope 
Print salary slip of the employee.


  
